snippet.title: System Shock - Pre-Alpha Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Return to Citadel Station and confront the horrors unleashed by a malevolent Artificial Intelligence in this complete remake of the genre defining classic from 1994. After 20 years Nightdive Studios is rebuilding System Shock from the ground up with a passionate team of veteran developers. 

May contain content inappropriate for children, visit www.esrb.org for rating information
